============================
PolyORB 17 NEW FEATURES LIST
============================

Copyright (C) 2015, AdaCore

This file contains a complete list of new features in version 17 of PolyORB.

An ISO date (YYYY-MM-DD) appears in parentheses after the description line.
This date shows the implementation date of the feature. Any 17 wavefront
subsequent to this date will contain the indicated feature, as will any
subsequent releases.

